                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-164-off894 t18240916-164-cd895"></join>, a half sovereign, four shillings and eight pence
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240916-164-victim1407" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Basham
                  <interp inst="t18240916-164-victim1407" type="surname" value="Basham"></interp>
